	<title>Dynamic network configuration using dhcp</title>
	<para>
	The clients are typically configured via the network configuration. Alternatively, the <emphasis role="strong">dhcpcd [network interface]</emphasis> tool can be used to configure the specified network interface via DHCP.
	</para>
